sentences.en: A jellyfish crop circle in Kingston Coombes, Oxfordshire.
sentences.cn: 一水母状麦田怪圈出现在牛津郡金士顿库姆斯.

sentences.en: He is living now in his mother's home county of Oxfordshire.
sentences.cn: 他现在居住在他母亲的故乡牛津郡。

sentences.en: His family have a country seat in Oxfordshire.
sentences.cn: 他家在牛津郡有一座乡间宅第。

sentences.en: Oxfordshire has always been an agricultural county, but some noted industries have appeared.
sentences.cn: 牛津郡向来以农业出名, 但是也曾经出现一些新兴的产业.

sentences.en: Oxfordshire is a county at the heart of England.
sentences.cn: 牛津郡是英国的重要地区,位于英国的中心地带.
